            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1286719</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>隨著語音辨識技術迅速進步，OpenAI 推出的「Whisper」已經成為眾多使用者心中的語音辨識首選。Whisper 以其強大的準確性和開源特性，成為免費且高效的自動生成字幕工具。然而安裝過程和操作方式仍然稍顯困難。今日小編會和大家分享一個全新的方法——WhisperDesktop。這個方法工具簡化原本繁瑣的操作流程，用户無需再使用指令，也能輕鬆進行語音辨識，自動生成字幕、文字稿等。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287380" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116200055-694x382.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="382" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116200055-694x382.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116200055.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲原本沒有字幕的影片</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287371" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116193937-694x471.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="471" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116193937-694x471.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116193937.jpg 909w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲使用今日介紹的 WhisperDesktop 後</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287375" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116200012-425x580.png" alt="" width="425" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116200012-425x580.png 425w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116200012.png 594w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 425px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲即可一鍵影片語音轉文字，還可以幫你加上 Timecode</p><h2>Step 1 下載 WhisperDesktop</h2><p>要使用 WhisperDesktop GUI，首先需要在 GitHub 下載桌面程式，截稿前最新版本為 1.12。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287288" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whisper_1-689x580.png" alt="" width="689" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whisper_1-689x580.png 689w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whisper_1.png 1069w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 689px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲請下載標明「Lastest」最新版本之程式</p><p>下載「WhisperDesktop.zip」壓縮檔（下圖綠框示）。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287291" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whisper2-694x396.png" alt="" width="694" height="396" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whisper2-694x396.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whisper2.png 1208w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲下載「WhisperDesktop.zip」</p><p>下載完畢後你需要解壓縮，解壓縮後你會看見文件夾內一共有 3 個檔案，其中有向日葵圖案的就是 WhisperDesktop 程式，不要移動其餘檔案，點擊即可開始設定，不過目前為止仍然未需要開啟「WhisperDesktop.exe」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287295" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whisper3-1-694x462.png" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whisper3-1-694x462.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whisper3-1.png 1169w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲以後只需點擊「向日葵」圖案即可使用</p><h2>Step 2 下載語言模組</h2><p>下載完 WhisperDesktop 後，並不代表我們可以立即使用這個程式語音轉文字。接下來我們需要到 Hugging Face 下載相關語言模型。（<a href="https://huggingface.co/ggerganov/whisper.cpp/tree/main">下載連結</a>）。甫打開模型庫會發覺琳瑯滿目，但如果你和小編一樣是業餘用途，就只需要選擇「Medium」模型。「Medium」模型兼顧準確性、生成速度及硬件需求，對一般用家來講算是夠用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287299" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116165930-605x580.jpg" alt="" width="605" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116165930-605x580.jpg 605w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116165930.jpg 938w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 605px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲打開模型庫時的畫面</p><p>同時按下 Ctrl+F，輸入 medium 後就可以馬上找到全部 medium 模型。今次小編會示範使用 ggml-medium.bin，點擊下圖紅色箭嘴指住的下載鍵即可開始下載「ggml-medium.bin」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287301" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whisper5-694x279.png" alt="" width="694" height="279" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whisper5-694x279.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whisper5.png 1269w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊紅色箭嘴指住的下載鍵下載 ggml-medium.bin（綠框示）</p><p>下載完成後，將「ggml-medium.bin」檔案移動至剛才有向日葵圖案「WhisperDesktop.exe」的文件夾。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287310" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116172542-694x459.png" alt="" width="694" height="459" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116172542-694x459.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116172542.png 1188w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲將 bin 檔移至 WhisperDesktop 的文件夾</p><h2>Step 3 開始設定 WhisperDesktop</h2><p>將「ggml-medium.bin」移動至 WhisperDesktop 文件夾後，你就可以開始設定 WhisperDesktop。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287311" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whisper6-694x460.png" alt="" width="694" height="460" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whisper6-694x460.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whisper6.png 1185w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊「向日葵」圖案使用</p><p>接下來你需要點擊「…」（紅箭嘴示）開啟你的 ggml。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287319" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116173350-694x466.png" alt="" width="694" height="466" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116173350-694x466.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116173350.png 860w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊「…」</p><p>載入剛才的 ggml-medium 模型。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287320" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116173542-694x385.png" alt="" width="694" height="385" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116173542-694x385.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116173542.png 1252w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲雙擊選擇剛才的模型</p><p>現時回到 WhisperDesktop，檢查 Model Path 是否剛才選擇的 ggml 模型，如正確就不要調整任何設定，保留其他設定為預設值後點擊「ok」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287330" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116180542-694x475.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="475" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116180542-694x475.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116180542.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲檢查 Model Path 是否剛才選擇的 ggml 模型，如正確就點擊 ok</p><h2>Step 4 開始使用</h2><p>稍等一陣就可載入完模型，之後你會看見下圖畫面，點擊「Language」選項，選擇「Chinese」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287331" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116181354-694x468.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="468" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116181354-694x468.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116181354.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲選擇「Chinese」</p><p>之後你可以在「Output Format」選擇輸出甚麼格式的文字稿：</p><ul><li>如果你要純文字逐字稿，可選擇「Text file」；</li><li>如果你想要生成 YouTube 的「CC 字幕」（有 Time Code），那麼就需要選擇「Subrip subtitles」輸出 SRT 檔案。</li></ul><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287355" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116185715-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116185715-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116185715.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲選擇所需格式</p><p>之後點擊「…」，選擇你需要轉為文字的影片。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287356" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116190241-694x469.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="469" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116190241-694x469.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116190241.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊「…」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287357" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116190406-694x385.png" alt="" width="694" height="385" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116190406-694x385.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116190406.png 1249w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲選擇所需影片</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287364" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116190629-694x472.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="472" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116190629-694x472.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116190629.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲選擇所需影片</p><p>選擇完影片後，點擊「Transcribe」開始語音轉文字。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287365" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116191739-694x469.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="469" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116191739-694x469.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116191739.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊「Transcribe」開始語音轉文字</p><h2>實測：轉換 15 分 25 秒 mp4 影片需時</h2><p>以下小編會使用一條 15 分 25 秒的 MP4 測試 WhisperDesktop 語音轉換文字的速度。小編使用的電腦為 ASUS Zenbook Flip 14，採用內置顯示卡。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287366" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116191813-422x580.png" alt="" width="422" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116191813-422x580.png 422w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116191813.png 528w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 422px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲小編測試影片長度為 15:25</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287365" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116191739-694x469.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="469" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116191739-694x469.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116191739.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊「Transcribe」開始語音轉文字</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287371" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116193937-694x471.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="471" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116193937-694x471.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116193937.jpg 909w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可在進度條檢查轉換進度</p><p>完成後會彈出一個提示視窗，告訴你耗時多久。WhisperDesktop 主要使用 GPU 轉錄為純文字，而由於小編的電腦沒有獨立顯示卡，因此耗時約 14 分鐘方完成。如果你的電腦顯示卡比較厲害，那麼可以用更短時間完成轉錄工作。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287372" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116195343-694x466.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="466" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116195343-694x466.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116195343.jpg 996w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲完成後會彈出視窗提示你</p><p>現在開啟影片所在文件夾，你會看見 .srt 檔案，這個就是你的 CC 字幕檔。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287369" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116193547-694x394.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="394" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116193547-694x394.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116193547.jpg 1172w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲生成的 .srt 字幕檔</p><p>普通點擊無法開啟 .srt 檔案，你需要選擇以「記事本」開啟。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287370" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116193806-694x515.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="515" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116193806-694x515.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116193806.jpg 881w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲選擇以「記事本」開啟 .srt 字幕檔</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287373" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116195420-277x580.png" alt="" width="277" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116195420-277x580.png 277w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116195420.png 429w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 277px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲現在你就可以看見你的 CC 字幕文字稿了</p><h2>總結：無須使用大量指令，圖形介面直觀完成工作</h2><p>對於那些不熟悉終端機指令的用户來説，WhisperDesktop 顯然是一個更具親和力的選擇。WhisperDesktop 簡化了安裝和操作過程，並將繁瑣的步驟圖像化，讓每個人都能輕鬆上手。</p><p>總結來説，Whisper GUI 是一款實用的工具，適合各類需求的用户。如果你曾因為難度較高的安裝或操作流程而放棄使用 Whisper，那麼這款 GUI 介面將無疑大幅簡化你的使用體驗，讓語音辨識過程更加順暢，無需過高電腦技術。</p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 傾傾科技背後黑暗事</p><p>========</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/01/22/whisper-gui-windows-free-to-use/ai/">【教學】AI 影片字幕製造機 WhisperDesktop    廣東話、外語片製 CC 字幕 + Windows 免費用</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
